    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/e5bdc5ba4732dd2939b8f4da47f0b262.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/e5bdc5ba4732dd2939b8f4da47f0b262.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/e5bdc5ba4732dd2939b8f4da47f0b262.mp4?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build, Automate, Autocast!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your factory build <strong>from scratch</strong> to autocast your spells!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/74f2e53630a607ed4beb56bf7f90d92b.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/74f2e53630a607ed4beb56bf7f90d92b.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enter the 20-Minute Battlefield</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive <strong>relentless waves</strong> of monsters against the clock!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/a6892e47c42b4300481b7891cc77a866.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/a6892e47c42b4300481b7891cc77a866.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master the Alchemical Spellbook</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't worry, the <strong>battle pauses</strong> while you’re building and browsing through recipes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/e4fc562d6efa19cb8a275ac7022e7bee.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/e4fc562d6efa19cb8a275ac7022e7bee.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stock up on<strong> factory parts</strong>, totems, power crystals, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/f66648e240a1426364fe052271717559.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/f66648e240a1426364fe052271717559.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Totem Synergies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Which <strong>golden totems</strong> will you draft? Can you <strong>unlock </strong>them all for your <strong>collection</strong>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/c6eddf12ea7c8b8246499baf660d103c.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/c6eddf12ea7c8b8246499baf660d103c.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Charms and Hexes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unpredictable <strong>boons </strong>and <strong>cursed zones </strong>require <strong>course-correction</strong> to keep the factory running.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/453376fd27e79ae99094374e01678d1d.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/453376fd27e79ae99094374e01678d1d.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Arcana Trials</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer <strong>10 Difficulty Levels </strong>filled with challenges and <strong>elite </strong>monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/da89470b3ea2acddbec51b03181ad260.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/da89470b3ea2acddbec51b03181ad260.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete the Collection</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ playable <strong>characters </strong>and<strong> 100+ totems</strong> await your discovery!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/c6a17347b56a1b2910c651b276b9e39c.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/c6a17347b56a1b2910c651b276b9e39c.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/a866be2f72414e7742a28d4db62366bc.poster.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/a866be2f72414e7742a28d4db62366bc.webm?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/a866be2f72414e7742a28d4db62366bc.mp4?t=1770207132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock all <strong>20+ playable characters</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over <strong>60 Spell Recipes</strong> to master!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draft from over <strong>100 Animal Totems</strong> to strengthen unique synergies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Mode</strong> after you survive the 20-minute battle!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb through <strong>10 Difficulty Levels</strong> in the <strong>Arcana Trials!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Daily Challenge Mode!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212630/extras/09596aff477e4c9ffeed86843d044e1e.avif?t=1770207132\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stop by our discord to leave feedback and share your builds! (Link to discord in the sidebar)</p>",
